=== INCLUSION-EXCLUSION for Paley p=11 ===
  c3 = 55
  3-cycles per vertex = 15
  3-cycles through QR pair: 3
  3-cycles through NQR pair: 3

  Formula: c3(comp) = 55 - 3*15 + q*3 + (3-q)*3 - n(V)
         = 10 + q*0 + 3*3 - n(V)
         = 19 + 0*q - n(V)

  QR-pair distribution:
    q=1, n(V)=1: 11 subsets, predicted c3(comp) = 18
    q=2, n(V)=0: 66 subsets, predicted c3(comp) = 19
    q=2, n(V)=1: 11 subsets, predicted c3(comp) = 18
    q=3, n(V)=0: 44 subsets, predicted c3(comp) = 19
    q=3, n(V)=1: 33 subsets, predicted c3(comp) = 18

  Verification against actual c3(comp):
    q=1, n(V)=1: actual=18, pred=18, match=True
    q=2, n(V)=0: actual=19, pred=19, match=True
    q=2, n(V)=1: actual=18, pred=18, match=True
    q=3, n(V)=0: actual=19, pred=19, match=True
    q=3, n(V)=1: actual=18, pred=18, match=True

  delta = 0: pair_qr = pair_nqr => c3(comp) constant iff n(V) constant

